Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.61,0:11:59.68,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,ピ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.17,0:12:01.88,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,じゃあもう帰るね
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.26,0:12:03.49,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,しずかちゃん
