Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.09,0:16:43.19,JP - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,決して異星人に
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.27,0:16:46.78,JP - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,道具を委ねてはならぬ
