Dialogue: 1,0:34:40.34,0:34:43.48,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,しずかちゃん　御免ね
Dialogue: 1,0:34:43.48,0:34:44.43,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,えっ
Dialogue: 1,0:34:45.59,0:34:47.52,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,僕はダメダメだっピけど
Dialogue: 1,0:34:48.65,0:34:51.00,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,これからも君を助けるっピ
Dialogue: 1,0:34:52.95,0:34:56.91,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,君がきっと　死んじゃったりなんかしなくていいように
Dialogue: 1,0:35:04.47,0:35:05.85,JP - down,Marina,0,0,0,,死ね
Dialogue: 1,0:35:07.76,0:35:11.88,JP - down,Marina,0,0,0,,放課後イジメ10連弾失敗するとか　ありえないんだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:35:13.19,0:35:15.51,JP - down,Marina,0,0,0,,マジあいつ何なの今週
Dialogue: 1,0:35:17.40,0:35:19.13,JP - down,Marina,0,0,0,,調子乗りやが
Dialogue: 1,0:35:30.69,0:35:34.95,JP - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,パパはお夕飯　あの人と食べるそうだから
Dialogue: 1,0:35:36.91,0:35:39.61,JP - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,まりちゃんももう少し
Dialogue: 1,0:35:39.61,0:35:42.17,JP - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,早く帰ってくれればいいのに
Dialogue: 1,0:35:43.00,0:35:46.58,JP - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,ママ　また一人で怒られちゃった
Dialogue: 1,0:35:47.60,0:35:52.09,JP - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,まりちゃん　まりちゃんはママの味方だよね
Dialogue: 1,0:35:54.56,0:35:58.76,JP - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,ママのお話　聞いてくれるよね
Dialogue: 1,0:35:59.63,0:36:00.57,JP - down,Marina,0,0,0,,うん
Comment: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:27.54,CN - down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:30.22,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,吶 那裡有什麼東西在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:33.47,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.38,0:00:38.53,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:01:00.79,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,肚子餓了噼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:14.61,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我是快樂星球的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:18.33,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,為了在宇宙裡傳播快樂正在旅行噼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.02,0:02:21.66,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我告別了故鄉快樂星球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.23,0:02:26.23,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,今天 我降落到這顆藍綠色的行星上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:29.17,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,但是差點被捉住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:32.70,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,有時還沒有食物吃真的太難噼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:37.47,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這個時候 靜香幫助了我噼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:40.24,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,非常感謝噼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:42.02,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麵包好好吃噼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.61,0:02:46.23,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,那真的是外星人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:50.06,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,你的名字是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:53.19,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,叫汪愛凱夫的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:56.66,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:02:59.62,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,汪愛凱夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:04.82,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 靜香她很困擾啊噼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.82,0:03:09.12,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊不不過 你叫我什麼隨你喜歡就好噼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:13.09,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,嗯 那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:15.59,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章魚噼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:21.31,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,既然靜香這麼叫了 那確實看起來挺適合的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:27.27,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,「四年級小學生」是靜香這種人類的「所屬」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:31.53,CN - down,Take,0,0,0,,對生物非常了解 而且很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.20,0:03:35.28,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,只要是看著靜香 就總感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:41.44,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜 靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.88,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,請務必讓我向你答謝噼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.92,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,「拍拍翅膀」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:52.92,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這是快樂道具其一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:56.46,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,使用的話就能在天空自由飛翔了噼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:06.10,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,就像這樣 就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:08.77,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,怎麼樣呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:16.33,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,來試試吧 接下來是靜香使用啦噼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:18.78,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,嗯 我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:21.05,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:24.32,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我還得去買「學生墊板」再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:25.44,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,欸 欸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:30.09,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,還有 麵包是午餐剩下的你不用太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:32.50,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,明天也會給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.04,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,為 為什麼噼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:36.74,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,明明這個很好玩的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:39.27,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,畢竟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:44.68,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,在空中飛行 也改變不了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:50.14,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,明天再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:56.75,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:58.94,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,難不成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:03.78,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,以前在天空中飛過的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:08.29,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,確實在這顆行星上 能飛的生物挺多的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:13.25,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,人類也會和鳥類混在一起 在夜晚進行飛行訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:17.92,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香 這個也是訓練的一項嗎噼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:21.51,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,不是 只是想靜靜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:25.95,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,學校畢竟有人在 看見了就會被抓去醫務室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:26.86,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:33.02,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,學校好像是靜香每天都要去的地方噼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:36.19,CN - down,Girl N,0,0,0,,然後啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:37.73,CN - down,Girl N,0,0,0,,和麻里奈說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:39.78,CN - down,Girl N,0,0,0,,我把她的學生墊板乾脆地折斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:43.70,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,好期待明天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:46.36,CN - down,Girl O,0,0,0,,這週已經是第三個板了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.45,CN - down,Girl J,0,0,0,,那傢伙又得去花錢買了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:50.88,CN - down,Girl M,0,0,0,,她還有沒有零用錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:51.91,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:55.36,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,還能用生活補助金買呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:00.29,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,她們看起來很開心噼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.67,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,是在商談去哪裡玩嗎噼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:05.77,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:09.97,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊 對啦噼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:12.95,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,今天我也要答謝你的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:15.73,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,今天的快樂道具是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:18.23,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,「快樂相機」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:21.06,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,雖然看似是普通的相機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:23.36,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,但像這樣拍下照片噼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:30.62,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,就會立刻列印這種「快樂相片」的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:32.75,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:36.82,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,但這樣的話用手機不是更好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:38.47,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,而且還挺重的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:39.95,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 但是但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:42.48,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這個相機擁有特別的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:45.38,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,是時候要去買墊板了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.08,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,文具店快要關門了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:49.88,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 今天也要買嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:52.81,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:57.57,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,它好像 又不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:06.86,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,明天再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:13.33,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香可是非常忙的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:17.58,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,即便如此 明天也一定要讓她開心起來噼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:22.42,CN - up,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:26.59,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這個是能在驚喜派對之類的地方使用的道具噼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:27.11,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:27.92,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:33.63,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,今天的麵包很甜噼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:34.67,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:39.23,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,正論官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:43.73,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這是隨時都能給出很好建議的朋友道具
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:45.35,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:50.44,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,今天的道具好厲害的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:53.03,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,是能發出土星兔子叫的原子筆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:56.23,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,啊 章魚噼 今天我得馬上回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:57.46,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:08:00.15,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 怎麼了噼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:02.34,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我得餵恰噼吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.46,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,恰噼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:06.50,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,唔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:08.76,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.30,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,要來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:14.81,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:16.68,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:21.44,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 這就是恰噼 好大噼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.36,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:27.08,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我明白了 我明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:30.15,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我回來啦 我回來啦 恰噼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:32.78,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香她笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:36.25,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.46,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,不能吃掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:46.38,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,今天我得負責喂它來著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.00,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,啊 你也可以進家裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:49.91,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:51.71,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,母親她已經去上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:55.04,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,說是要同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:57.98,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 同伴是什麼噼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:09:00.72,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,就是「同客人陪伴進店」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:03.27,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,感覺挺忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:06.15,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊嘞 你的爸爸在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:10.45,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,沒有爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:17.29,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,人類只用靠媽媽就能生孩子嗎噼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:19.20,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,好厲害噼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:25.25,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,恰噼從我小時候開始就一直陪著我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:28.48,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,是爸爸留在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:31.96,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我最喜歡恰噼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:33.34,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:36.77,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,只要有恰噼 我就沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:39.83,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,其它我什麼都不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:43.35,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,發生什麼都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:49.66,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,無論多麼痛苦 多麼難受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:53.36,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,稍微有點臭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:57.69,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊 感覺好焦躁不安 這是什麼感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:10:01.52,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊嘞 結果她有爸爸啊噼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.78,0:10:06.13,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,吶 快樂星球在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:09.17,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 從這裡看不到噼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:11.38,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,非常遙遠的地方噼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:15.30,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,快樂星球上到處都長滿了「快樂水果」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:17.22,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,那可非常好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:20.47,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香你也可以來玩哦噼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:22.95,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我去不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:27.04,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,別這麼說噼 只要坐快樂飛船就能飛到噼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:30.15,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我並不相信魔法什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:32.36,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,不是魔法 是快樂道具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:34.40,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,去不了的 無論什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.39,0:10:39.53,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,不論是快樂星球 還是爸爸那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:51.09,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,我所愛的孩子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:54.17,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,請使用這些快樂道具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:57.42,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,在宇宙中傳播快樂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:03.29,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,但是要注意 絕對不能「打破規則」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.48,0:11:09.14,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,媽媽 別說是規則 我現在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:12.28,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,連讓她使用道具都還做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:14.78,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:18.27,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我希望靜香她能夠多笑一笑噼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:21.14,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:25.04,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,今後我會邀請你去到快樂星球的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:28.33,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我還有很多快樂道具的噼 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:30.13,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,都說了那些魔法什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:31.63,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,所以定會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:36.09,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,讓靜香你綻放最美好的笑容噼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:44.33,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊 因為某些原因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:48.35,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我暫時還回不去 現在沒辦法馬上出發
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:51.92,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,但是肯定總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:53.36,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章魚噼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:56.76,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章魚噼沒什麼氣味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:57.87,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:11:59.68,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:01.88,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,那我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:03.49,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.26,0:12:09.81,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,明天再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.05,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:28.01,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這麼快就來了嗎 我在等你呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:31.65,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,今天會給你一個 我珍藏的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:34.36,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,你的臉上好像有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.36,0:12:37.74,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊 那是恰噼的項圈呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:41.90,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,和朋友打架了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:46.66,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊 人類打架過後臉的顏色就會發生變化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:49.76,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我害羞的時候 也會變得通紅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:53.50,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,對了對了 既然如此 我有一個推薦的道具噼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:55.67,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,「和好絲帶」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:57.26,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這個怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:01.60,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,只要靜香和朋友用這個道具分別纏住小指
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:04.50,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,很快就能和好如初了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:08.44,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊 它很結實還可以無限延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:11.28,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,無論多遠的朋友也請放心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:15.82,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,好好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.20,0:13:19.15,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,好想用它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:22.51,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,真的嗎噼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:23.49,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,那麼趕緊去朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:26.51,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我想自己一個人慢慢使用它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:28.02,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,能借我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:28.88,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:30.54,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:33.29,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,快樂道具的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:40.13,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,使用道具的時候 必須要在快樂星人視線之內使用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:45.27,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,絕對不能把道具委託給外星人的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:48.70,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,拜託了 章魚噼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:53.94,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,即便如此這是靜香的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:59.55,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,借你啦 如果有不懂的地方隨時可以來問我噼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:01.07,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:04.73,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,希望你能和朋友和好如初噼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:06.25,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:10.83,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:22.35,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,因為她是靜香 所以我應該不用擔心噼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:33.73,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,感覺噼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:43.49,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,只是有點擔心她而已噼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:52.05,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,只是有點而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:57.58,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,有沒有和好我才不會在意呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:15:02.96,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,絲帶會無線延伸 經常會出現被纏繞住的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:06.97,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,那樣的話一個人就更麻煩了噼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:09.78,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我得去幫幫她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:13.42,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:45.55,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香 你在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:50.38,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,那條絲帶 繫在房梁上是沒什麼用的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:54.77,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我再和你說一下使用方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:59.48,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,沒事的 你可以下來了 靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:02.48,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:04.53,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:05.24,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:20.49,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,她死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:22.50,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:26.42,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,為什麼 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:29.80,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,為什麼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:35.31,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香她死了噼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:40.38,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我的絲帶 明明是為了和好用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.09,0:16:43.19,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,絕對不能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:46.78,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,把道具委託給外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:55.13,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,規則 是我打破的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:26.43,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:30.69,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:43.08,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,在整個宇宙之中 死亡被公平且平等地規定著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.66,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,沒有任何手段能夠顛覆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:50.13,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,無論是多麼睿智的道具也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:52.72,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,讓死者復活是做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:17:59.08,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.96,0:18:04.67,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,只要用這個相機拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:08.40,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,就會立刻列印這種「快樂相片」的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.68,0:18:11.48,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,但是這樣用手機不是更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:17.45,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,但是靜香 這個相機有個特別的功能噼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:20.12,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,「時間相機」的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:23.99,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,雖然保存的相片只有一張噼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:27.06,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,但要是把相片用相機讀取後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:30.60,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,「就能回到」這張照片拍攝的瞬間時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:38.32,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,從快樂星球到達這裡的第七天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:41.74,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,太陽系第三行星 地球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:45.98,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,智慧生命體 人類
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:52.59,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,在你們的言語裡 自絕性命應該是被稱為「自殺」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:56.36,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,為什麼會存在這種行為呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:18:59.95,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,為什麼你要選擇自殺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:02.61,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我並不知道原因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:07.54,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,但是 因為不知道 所以想聽你講
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:12.04,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,和你說很多的話 了解更多的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:17.51,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,想和你一起思考出 你能活下去的未來噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:20.18,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香 你一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:22.87,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,在明天能 笑出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:34.61,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章魚噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:40.60,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,突然怎麼了呢 你拿著相機呆住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:44.25,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:48.99,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:53.49,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,是 是的呢 相機我拿著噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:55.26,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,照片拍攝好了噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:57.38,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:00.97,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章魚噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:04.35,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,沒什麼噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:05.52,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:08.22,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,啊 是時候要去買墊板了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:09.10,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:10.87,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,文具店要關門了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:11.98,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,那我就去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:13.15,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,等會噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:14.38,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:18.78,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,必須要知道更多關於靜香的事情噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:24.40,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,首先是靜香每天都會說的地方 記得名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.71,0:20:26.92,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.48,0:20:28.83,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我從明天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:35.34,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,希望你能帶我一起去學校噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:42.78,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這裡是學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:46.82,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,在這裡的話 就能更加了解靜香噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:49.39,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:51.54,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,早啊 寄生蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:52.65,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:55.43,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,是之前在公園見到的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.43,0:20:57.65,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,寄生蟲是什麼意思呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:00.79,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,今天也好臭呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.79,0:21:01.42,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:03.83,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,和那條臭水溝裡的狗一樣的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:08.33,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜 靜香 你 你還好嗎噼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:13.60,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,學校 你要來也可以 但被發現就會被抓去醫務室的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:15.67,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:17.42,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,花朵髮簪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:23.16,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這要把這個插在頭上 周圍的人就會看到我是朵快樂花噼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:24.91,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,快樂花是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:32.29,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,為什麼你頭上帶著折耳根花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.72,0:21:33.82,CN - down,Friend A,0,0,0,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:35.09,CN - down,Friend B,0,0,0,,真土鱉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:43.61,CN - down,Teacher,0,0,0,,要開始上課了 快回到座位坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.31,0:21:48.70,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,總而言之 首先要了解在學校的靜香噼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:51.59,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,也許這樣就能知道她自殺的原因了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:59.12,CN - down,Teacher,0,0,0,,這個問題的話 久世你來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:05.22,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,老師 久世同學說她的作業忘記帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.65,0:22:08.97,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,不 我的筆記本是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:12.57,CN - down,Teacher,0,0,0,,什麼啊這樣 那就東你來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.44,0:22:23.03,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我明白了噼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:27.63,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香因為忘記帶作業而悲傷 所以選擇了自殺噼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:31.50,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,那就看我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.06,0:22:36.01,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章魚噼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.01,0:22:36.75,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:40.38,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,明天作業的答案第一題是35
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:43.24,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,第二題是162
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.24,0:22:44.72,CN - down,Teacher,0,0,0,,正確
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.92,0:22:48.40,CN - down,Teacher,0,0,0,,那麼下一個問題 雲母坂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.40,0:22:51.30,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,欸 啊 那 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:54.99,CN - down,Teacher,0,0,0,,什麼你忘記做了嗎 那就東你來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.36,0:23:03.86,CN - down,Friend A,0,0,0,,已經是午休時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:06.11,CN - down,Friend B,0,0,0,,每次都剩飯剩菜不覺得愧疚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:10.99,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,沒有罪惡感真的了不起啊 反正你連伙食費都沒交呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.47,0:23:13.25,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊嘞 又來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.28,0:23:18.50,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,因為沒有吃完午餐而傷心 於是靜香自殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.13,0:23:20.25,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.74,0:23:21.95,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.95,0:23:22.96,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章魚噼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.51,0:23:25.50,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.04,0:23:45.40,CN - down,Friend A,0,0,0,,這傢伙連玉米的棒子都吃下去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:47.29,CN - down,Friend B,0,0,0,,恐 恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:50.68,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這樣就沒問題啦噼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.00,0:25:06.43,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊嘞 這難不成是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.66,0:25:08.98,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,如果沒猜錯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.42,0:25:14.41,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香和麻里奈是在吵架嗎噼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.52,0:25:23.38,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,快樂星人要是吵架 就會把對方的快樂紙張藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.95,0:25:28.40,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這是為了引起對方注意 從而促進和好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.16,0:25:32.64,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈把筆記本藏起來是一樣的吧噼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.58,0:25:36.85,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,而且她一直盯著靜香看 也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.85,0:25:39.68,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,她想和靜香和好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.11,0:25:44.40,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,那叫 吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.00,0:25:47.73,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.73,0:25:49.79,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,果然是啊噼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.11,0:25:53.73,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,既然如此就要盡快和好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.30,0:25:57.07,CN - down,Friend A,0,0,0,,啊 你在這啊 久世同學
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.07,0:25:59.25,CN - down,Friend B,0,0,0,,麻里奈有話要和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.25,0:26:01.76,CN - down,Friend C,0,0,0,,午休的時候 在體育館倉庫那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.01,0:26:06.33,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,是機會噼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.71,0:26:11.34,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.64,0:26:15.34,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,你還不去嗎 麻里奈她在等你的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.48,0:26:20.09,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,去 很快就會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.87,0:26:24.99,CN - down,Tokopi,0,0,0,,和好的秘訣 是要和對方好好說話噼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.67,0:26:28.77,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,因為交談可以產生快樂的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.47,0:26:33.36,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章魚噼你根本沒有和麻里奈說過話
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.36,0:26:35.20,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,所以你才會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.54,0:26:38.97,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 這種事情 噼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.70,0:26:46.44,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,難不成 是因為吵的架非常兇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.44,0:26:49.44,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,比如說擅自吃掉對方的快樂布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.02,0:26:52.51,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,但是必須要和好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.88,0:26:53.75,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.40,0:26:56.61,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.08,0:27:02.85,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,「變身調色盤」
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.35,0:27:06.94,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,只需要放入靜香身體的一部分 按下開關
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.86,0:27:18.17,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,就能變身成為對方的樣子噼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.17,0:27:19.28,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.98,0:27:22.02,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香你就在廁所等著我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.02,0:27:24.57,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我去和她嘮閒聊噼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.28,0:27:30.13,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,由我代替靜香 讓兩人和好如初吧噼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.18,0:27:33.17,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.68,0:27:37.75,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,就算再嚴重的吵架 只要好好溝通的話 肯定能
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.75,0:27:39.93,CN - down,ShizuPi,0,0,0,,對 對不起噼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.93,0:27:43.20,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,你那是什麼說話方式 好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.20,0:27:45.36,CN - down,ShizuPi,0,0,0,,那 那個 麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.36,0:27:48.15,CN - down,ShizuPi,0,0,0,,正好我也有話要和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.52,0:28:00.99,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,我討厭你這種噁心的說話
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.99,0:28:03.27,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,別給我再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.27,0:28:05.62,CN - down,ShizuPi,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉噼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.70,0:28:13.47,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,突然變動漫宅了 什麼我什麼噼的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.47,0:28:16.63,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,你個種我早就知道噁心了 聽了就討厭就張你那破嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.63,0:28:18.88,CN - down,ShizuPi,0,0,0,,對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.88,0:28:21.22,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,所以 想和你說說話
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.22,0:28:23.86,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,你這傢伙最近 牙{\fn等线\b1\fs69}䶪䶪{\fn方正锐正黑_GBK ExtraBold}了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.86,0:28:25.46,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,午餐什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.46,0:28:26.39,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.10,0:28:29.38,CN - up,Marina,0,0,0,,明明連稅金都從未繳納過
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.10,0:28:30.81,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,雖然說是談談 但臉蛋熱熱的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.38,0:28:33.01,CN - up,Marina,0,0,0,,還有作業也是自信滿滿地回答
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.16,0:28:35.90,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,在快樂星球上不會有人這麼大力觸碰自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.59,0:28:35.53,CN - up,Marina,0,0,0,,裝知識分子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.22,0:28:37.82,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,站不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.40,0:28:40.46,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,感覺眼淚要
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.55,0:28:42.60,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.60,0:28:43.42,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.49,0:28:46.79,CN - up,ShizuPi,0,0,0,,沒什
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.49,0:28:46.79,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.84,0:28:52.59,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,好好把話聽完
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.90,0:28:56.67,CN - down,ShizuPi,0,0,0,,麻里奈 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.45,0:29:01.55,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,別隨便叫我名字
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.35,0:29:05.57,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,淫蕩會傳染的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.47,0:29:12.31,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.21,0:29:15.68,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,好怕好怕好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.49,0:29:20.47,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,好痛好痛 聲音發不出來噼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.47,0:29:23.99,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,好痛苦 好想哭 好想逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.08,0:29:33.96,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.60,0:29:37.12,CN - down,ShizuPi,0,0,0,,麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.04,0:29:43.22,CN - down,ShizuPi,0,0,0,,那個 雖然我不知道為什麼你要這麼對我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.77,0:29:46.68,CN - down,ShizuPi,0,0,0,,但是只要能好好交談肯定能理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.68,0:29:47.44,CN - down,ShizuPi,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.44,0:29:49.52,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,只有你最沒有資格這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.66,0:29:52.53,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,你這種敗類
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.48,0:30:02.46,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,靠男人吃飯生活的「雞蛋」擱這立貞潔牌坊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.46,0:30:04.20,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,把我爸爸給還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.74,0:30:10.12,CN - down,ShizuPi,0,0,0,,麻 麻里奈 等會
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.12,0:30:13.29,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,都說了 別這樣跟我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.29,0:30:14.79,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊 這下
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.13,0:30:16.29,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.59,0:30:20.13,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章魚噼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.00,0:30:30.77,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,明天的作業答案是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.77,0:30:32.51,CN - down,Students,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.44,0:30:38.54,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈為什麼要做那些事呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.79,0:30:41.61,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,對了 確實
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.87,0:30:44.48,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,你最近 是不是得寸進尺了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.48,0:30:45.82,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,午餐什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.66,0:30:51.33,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,還有作業 自信滿滿地回答呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.33,0:30:52.55,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.15,0:30:54.55,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,難不成
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.07,0:30:58.43,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,第二題是162
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.66,0:31:04.60,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,是我的錯嗎噼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.95,0:31:10.91,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,那 我就去了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.64,0:31:23.86,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,因為我的錯讓靜香遭殃了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.76,0:31:27.87,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,果然 我應該代替她去的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.54,0:31:32.47,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這次說不定 能夠順利和好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.84,0:31:34.75,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,要趕緊去噼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.75,0:31:36.08,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,去噼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.56,0:31:51.82,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,恐懼到我一步都走不動噼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.39,0:31:55.10,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,明明要幫助靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.10,0:31:57.16,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,明明想替代她痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.60,0:32:00.17,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,是我太懦弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.48,0:32:05.86,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.08,0:32:19.78,CN - down,ShizuPi,0,0,0,,老師 老師 有誰能幫幫
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.78,0:32:21.77,CN - down,ShizuPi,0,0,0,,在體育館倉庫
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.38,0:32:25.00,CN - down,ShizuPi,0,0,0,,幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.63,0:32:31.09,CN - down,Naoki,0,0,0,,要是有我能幫得上儘管提吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.94,0:32:34.48,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,嗯 東君
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.48,0:32:37.52,CN - down,Naoki,0,0,0,,要把這個作為下次班級會議的議題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.52,0:32:39.90,CN - down,Naoki,0,0,0,,就在下週三
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.27,0:32:44.68,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,嗯 我真的沒什麼事 那就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.68,0:32:47.24,CN - down,Naoki,0,0,0,,要 要不要和其他的老師商量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.74,0:32:52.63,CN - down,Naoki,0,0,0,,比如體育老師保土谷 我在學生會上經常見到
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.63,0:32:54.04,CN - down,Naoki,0,0,0,,那個人稍微有些可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.04,0:32:56.06,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,反正不會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.06,0:32:57.21,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.55,0:33:01.63,CN - down,Naoki,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.43,0:33:17.15,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,剛剛的男生不管他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.15,0:33:18.35,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.35,0:33:20.15,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這樣啊噼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.67,0:33:29.91,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.91,0:33:32.36,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,是章魚噼幫助我的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.34,0:33:35.76,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,老師感覺不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.76,0:33:39.39,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,明明是久世來呼救 卻是久世被毆打
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.15,0:33:43.69,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,多虧了你我只有臉受了點傷
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.04,0:33:47.08,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 靜香 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.08,0:33:51.53,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,其它的也是 很多都是你做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.53,0:33:55.67,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,知道作業的答案 還有午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.67,0:33:57.60,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,消失的筆記本也出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.31,0:34:01.64,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,不對的噼 正是因為如此靜香今天
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.64,0:34:04.31,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,才會被這麼痛打的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.74,0:34:10.73,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,學校的話 自從麻里奈的爸爸和我的媽媽關係變好之後
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.73,0:34:12.82,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,生活一直這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.62,0:34:17.95,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我只能在旁怯懦地看著 卻什麼也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.74,0:34:19.83,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.35,0:34:22.87,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,沒什麼值得快樂的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.87,0:34:27.69,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,畢竟有麻里奈在 淨是些討厭的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.45,0:34:30.59,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.43,0:34:36.22,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,最近稍微覺得沒那麼壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.34,0:34:43.48,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.48,0:34:44.43,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.59,0:34:47.52,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,雖然我是沒用的章魚噼
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.65,0:34:51.00,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,但我今後會一直幫助你的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.95,0:34:56.91,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,你的話肯定 不必向死而行了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.47,0:35:05.85,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.76,0:35:11.88,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,放學後欺凌十發連續失敗 簡直不可置信
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.19,0:35:15.51,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,真的是那傢伙這週到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.40,0:35:19.13,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,得寸進尺
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.69,0:35:34.95,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,爸爸晚上 又和那個人出去吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.91,0:35:39.61,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,麻里要是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.61,0:35:42.17,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,稍微早點回來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.00,0:35:46.58,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,媽媽我 又一個人被挨罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.60,0:35:52.09,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,麻里 麻里你站在媽媽這邊對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.56,0:35:58.76,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,媽媽的話 你會聽的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.63,0:36:00.57,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,嗯
